The rifle also has a claw scope mount on it and also has a custom rubberized pistol grip and also has an h&k muzzle break and new h&k rollers If your looking for a cheap but reliable and accurate .308 battle rifle this is the gun for you! Once in a great while something comes along that is so obvious that it makes you say “Why didn’t I think of that?” The Velocity LR (Long Rib) concept is exactly that. We asked ourselves why a semi-auto barrel rib starts at the front of the receiver, a full 4 ½” further forward than an over-and-under shotgun. 

Doesn't that unnecessarily shorten the sighting plane? The answer is yes, but we can do better. The new Velocity LR has an innovative ramp style fixed rib that starts at the back of the receiver giving the shooter the maximum length sighting plane for better target acquisition and tracking. The bottom line is that a better sight picture equals more broken targets.

The Velocity LR combines all of the other ground breaking innovations that have made the XLR5 Velocity so popular last year. FABARM Velocity LR – Moving Forward Faster.
